temperature.

00:38:24.160 --> 00:38:25.690
That's not the exciting one.

00:38:25.690 --> 00:38:28.276
The exciting one is--

00:38:28.276 --> 00:38:31.050
if I can get it out.

00:38:31.050 --> 00:38:35.000
What happens to the
polynorbornene?

00:38:35.000 --> 00:38:37.310
This is the sad ball, the one
that wouldn't bounce at room

00:38:37.310 --> 00:38:38.440
temperature.

00:38:38.440 --> 00:38:41.625
By raising its use temperature
