-We're all so proud of you!

00:41:56.352 --> 00:42:00.531
Proud, proud, proud, proud,
proud, proud.

00:42:00.531 --> 00:42:02.004
What are you going to do now?

00:42:02.004 --> 00:42:04.459
-I was going to go upstairs
for a minute.

00:42:04.459 --> 00:42:05.812
-I mean with your future?

00:42:05.812 --> 00:42:07.105
Your life?

00:42:07.105 --> 00:42:08.896
'Well, that's a little
hard to say.

