-Ben.

00:42:09.800 --> 00:42:11.440
-Excuse me.

00:42:11.440 --> 00:42:13.880
-Mr. McGuire?

00:42:13.880 --> 00:42:15.734
-Ben.

00:42:15.734 --> 00:42:17.198
-Mr. McGuire.

00:42:17.198 --> 00:42:18.180
-Come with me for a minute.

00:42:18.180 --> 00:42:18.880
PROFESSOR: See the lipstick?

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:20.396
-I want to talk to you.

00:42:20.396 --> 00:42:22.680
Excuse us, Joanne.

00:42:22.680 --> 00:42:24.280
PROFESSOR: See, it's the '60s.

00:42:24.280 --> 00:42:25.390
They blow off the ladies.

00:42:25.390 --> 00:42:26.640
Now the men are going to talk.

00:42:32.775 --> 00:42:35.260
-I just want to say
one word to you.

00:42:35.260 --> 00:42:38.655
Just one word.

00:42:38.655 --> 00:42:40.110
-Yes, sir?

00:42:40.110 --> 00:42:40.595
-Are you listening?

00:42:40.595 --> 00:42:42.550
-Yes, I am.

