-Plastics.

00:42:47.030 --> 00:42:49.010
-Exactly how do you mean?

00:42:49.010 --> 00:42:51.440
-There's a great future
in plastics.

00:42:51.440 --> 00:42:52.890
Think about it.

00:42:52.890 --> 00:42:53.580
Will you think about it?

00:42:53.580 --> 00:42:54.350
-Yes, I will.

00:42:54.350 --> 00:42:55.850
-Enough said.

